{"tid":665374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強硬獨派當選加泰新主席  誓言獨立建國","createTime":"2018-05-15T01:41:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T00:34:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c6c314ad48eadf524e6a8d65e2aa7ea51e81c63","tid":665374,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:41:39.000Z","msg":"（星島日報報道）西班牙加泰隆尼亞自治區的議會昨日選出強硬獨派托拉（Quim Torra）為新主席，意味着西班牙當局將結束七個月來對加泰的直接統治。托拉誓言爭取建立一個獨立國家。<br />\n<br />\n分歧甚深的加泰議會，以六十六票贊成、六十五票反對及四票棄權，選出托拉任加泰新主席。西班牙憲法法院此前裁定，加泰去年十月一日的獨立公投違憲，但托拉周一在議會表決前致辭時表明，他將遵守公投的結果，全力爭取「建立一個共和國形式的獨立國家」。<br />\n<br />\n五十五歲的托拉是加泰前主席普伊格蒙特欽點的人選。普伊格蒙特因推動加泰獨立而流亡德國，被西班牙政府以叛亂罪通緝。托拉成功出線，仍尋求脫離西班牙獨立，料更添政治不明朗因素。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1801482&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1801482%26target%3D2&d=kJqg1kpVOanmZM9Z9Y77dgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=eaa8ac8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1801482%26target%3D2&h=9e6b6981\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1801482&amp;target=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a039a25545cabbca1d4af90d48cb4f9d5677472","tid":665374,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:53:52.000Z","msg":"唔擁護一個西班牙，仲唔好似支那咁dq佢？"},{"pid":"ecbc3fb276418b4c5fa5a78f024525983b588e80","tid":665374,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T02:16:55.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81856f0b197e89dfb9fb6dc8cc09b802a836c70","tid":665374,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike"